# Groth16 build artifacts. snarkjs setup is NOT bit-for-bit reproducible (the
# contribution mixes OS randomness), so the canonical BLEND proving key + witness
# generator + verification key are committed as a MATCHED set — proving works
# out-of-the-box and the vkey always matches the zkey.
#
# The larger composite artifacts + shared ptau are regenerated by
# `pnpm circom:setup` (SEFI_CIRCUITS=composite_borrow_exit).
build/*.ptau
build/*.r1cs
build/*.sym
build/composite_borrow_exit.zkey
build/composite_borrow_exit_js/
# Committed matched set for blend (the on-chain-wired recipe):
!build/blend_utilization.zkey
!build/blend_utilization.vkey.json
!build/composite_borrow_exit.vkey.json
!build/blend_utilization_js/
!build/blend_utilization_js/**
